I made a Digital Literacy Awareness infographic with Canva. Canva is a tool that is easy to use. 
My infographic talks about Digital Literacy. It says what Digital Literacy is. It also says what 
digital tools are good for students. It tells people how to be safe on the internet. It teaches 
people how to look online and how to write good emails.

The infographic wants to teach students that they need to be good at using technology and be 
responsible when they are online. This is because we live in a world that uses a lot of technology. 
It says that tools like Google Drive and GitHub and Canva can help people get things done faster. 
It also says that people need to be safe by using strong passwords and not falling for phishing scams.

One thing I liked about this task was learning how to show information using pictures of a lot of words.
The hard part was figuring out how information to put on the infographic without making it too crowded. 
This task taught me that it is important to communicate using pictures and visuals. Digital Literacy is important. 
I learned a lot about it by making this infographic, about Digital Literacy.

